#. <section class="sutta" id="an4.96"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an4.96:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 4"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 4"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an4.96:0.2"
msgid "10. Asuravagga"
msgstr "10. Demons"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an4.96:0.3"
msgid "96. Rāgavinayasutta"
msgstr "96. Removing Greed"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an4.96:1.1"
msgid "“Cattārome, bhikkhave, puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr "“Mendicants, these four people are found in the world."

msgctxt "an4.96:1.2"
msgid "Katame cattāro?"
msgstr "What four?"

msgctxt "an4.96:1.3"
msgid ""
"Attahitāya paṭipanno no parahitāya, parahitāya paṭipanno no attahitāya, "
"nevattahitāya paṭipanno no parahitāya, attahitāya ceva paṭipanno parahitāya "
"ca."
msgstr ""
"~One who practices to benefit themselves, but not others; ~one who practices "
"to benefit others, but not themselves; ~one who practices to benefit neither "
"themselves nor others; and ~one who practices to benefit both themselves and "
"others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "an4.96:2.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya paṭipanno hoti no parahitāya?"
msgstr "And how does a person practice to benefit themselves, but not others?"

msgctxt "an4.96:2.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā rāgavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, no paraṃ "
"rāgavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person practices to remove their own greed, hate, and delusion, "
"but doesn’t encourage others to do the same."

msgctxt "an4.96:2.3"
msgid "attanā dosavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, no paraṃ dosavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:2.4"
msgid "attanā mohavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, no paraṃ mohavinayāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:2.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāya."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit themselves, but not others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an4.96:3.1"
msgid "Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo parahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no attahitāya?"
msgstr "And how does a person practice to benefit others, but not themselves?"

msgctxt "an4.96:3.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā na rāgavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, paraṃ "
"rāgavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person doesn’t practice to remove their own greed, hate, and "
"delusion, but encourages others to remove theirs."

msgctxt "an4.96:3.3"
msgid "attanā na dosavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, paraṃ dosavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:3.4"
msgid "attanā na mohavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, paraṃ mohavinayāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:3.5"
msgid "Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo parahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no attahitāya."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit others, but not themselves."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
msgctxt "an4.96:4.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo nevattahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāya?"
msgstr ""
"And how does a person practice to benefit neither themselves nor others?"

msgctxt "an4.96:4.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā na rāgavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, no "
"paraṃ rāgavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person doesn’t practice to remove their own greed, hate, and "
"delusion, nor do they encourage others to remove theirs."

msgctxt "an4.96:4.3"
msgid ""
"attanā na dosavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, no paraṃ dosavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:4.4"
msgid ""
"attanā na mohavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, no paraṃ mohavinayāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:4.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo nevattahitāya paṭipanno hoti, no parahitāya."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit neither themselves nor others."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi2.97"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "an4.96:5.1"
msgid ""
"Kathañca, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya ceva paṭipanno hoti parahitāya ca?"
msgstr "And how does a person practice to benefit both themselves and others?"

msgctxt "an4.96:5.2"
msgid ""
"Idha, bhikkhave, ekacco puggalo attanā ca rāgavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, "
"parañca rāgavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""
"It’s when a person practices to remove their own greed, hate, and delusion, "
"and encourages others to remove theirs."

msgctxt "an4.96:5.3"
msgid "attanā ca dosavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, parañca dosavinayāya samādapeti;"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:5.4"
msgid "attanā ca mohavinayāya paṭipanno hoti, parañca mohavinayāya samādapeti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an4.96:5.5"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ kho, bhikkhave, puggalo attahitāya ceva paṭipanno hoti parahitāya ca."
msgstr "That’s how a person practices to benefit both themselves and others."

msgctxt "an4.96:5.6"
msgid "Ime kho, bhikkhave, cattāro puggalā santo saṃvijjamānā lokasmin”ti."
msgstr "These are the four people found in the world.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an4.96:5.7"
msgid "Chaṭṭhaṃ."
msgstr ""
